    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels. The single deficiency (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is accepted given established regulatory precedent for single-condition ASTM F1717 testing and the conservative nature of the prescribed load level. Overall model risk level 3 credibility requirements are judged satisfied.",
